data.description: Motivated sellers don't miss out, this one will not last!!! Come see this beautiful tri-level home, hidden gem located in well sought out unincorporated Crystal Lake. Are you outdoorsy, enjoy nature, love to boat? Boating dock 2 minutes away, enjoy the winter and summer amenities Crystal Lake Park District has to offer. From ice fishing during the winter to boating, kayaking or jet skiing during the summer. This spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom + bonus room, immaculate maintained home is move in ready. This winter sip on some hot chocolate with family and friends over a bonfire on a newer extended deck. During summer, soak up the sun at Crystal Lake West Beach or simply enjoy your backyard oasis. Vaulted ceilings, newer wood laminate flooring throughout home, radon mitigation system installed, sump pump and yearly maintenance of septic tank. Carpets will be professional cleaned, 1 year home warranty and invisible dog fence with 2 collars will be included.
